<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> matirai koṇṭa kopparake<hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>ri pa<hi rend="grantha">nma</hi>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rkku yāṇṭu Irupattāṟāvatu vaṭakarai nalvayalūr
<lb n="3"/>kūṟṟattu tevatāṉam Uṟumurc ciṟuttirukkoyil
<lb n="4"/>p perumāṉaṭikaḷukku koṟṟamaṅkalattu maṉṟā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṭi nakkaṉ ṟūṅkānai maṇavāṭṭi kovaṭi nili
<lb n="6"/>Aṭṭiṉa Āṭu toṇṇūṟu Ivvāṭu koṇ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṭu nicatam Uḻakku neyyāl Oru nantāviḷa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>kku <hi rend="grantha">cantrāditya</hi>vaṟ Erippomāṉom U(ṟ)ṟumur <hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>
<lb n="9" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">bhai</hi>yom Itu <hi rend="grantha">panmāheśvara</hi>(ri)ra<hi rend="grantha">kṣai <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi>
</p>

